{"id": 778, "genre": 1001, "title": "你都如何感知传说中的霸王级大寒潮？", "description": "“太阳已不是太阳，只是冰箱里的灯。”", "record_count": 5087, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160607194459wtHVumgTDsoQiK9W.jpeg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-01-23T01:00:58Z", "options": [{"id": 43521, "content": "广东下雪了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 437309}, {"id": 44033, "content": "水管被冻住了，滴水不出！", "image": "img/option/option/20160702200902aBiIlo95TWRmt2E7.JPG", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 396096}, {"id": 43268, "content": "我要去南半球", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 423374}, {"id": 46085, "content": "爬黄山回来 困在高速上12小时", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 453104}, {"id": 43271, "content": "只能说  请叫我神棍", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 423731}, {"id": 43272, "content": "?這天氣一起陪你出去玩的都是真愛 ?", "image": null, "praise_count": 29, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 103719}, {"id": 43528, "content": "广州一天内风、雨、雪、霰全齐了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 400760}, {"id": 43273, "content": "速凍下 生活在《魔都》依然沸腾照樣 嗨～", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 103719}, {"id": 43529, "content": "已经窝了两天了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 191609}, {"id": 43274, "content": "到家开了空调 结果发现 姨妈巾没了 跑出去买~ 折腾了一个多小时 回家发现 空调温度 只上涨了1°....【是我空调坏了吗？】", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 251751}, {"id": 43275, "content": "冻在床上下不了了", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 115503}, {"id": 43531, "content": "广东下雪啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 310777}, {"id": 43278, "content": "#+*+#+**/+##┐┑┟∷U……刚才冻得手抖，现在捂了半天没反应，用僵硬的手打出按出来了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 238601}, {"id": 43790, "content": "啪啪啪不敢脱裤子", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 436602}, {"id": 43279, "content": "聽說；速凍天氣和音浪更配額 ?^^✌?️", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 103719}, {"id": 43792, "content": "来自南方的我在家里觉得冰箱里会更暖和一些", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 438938}, {"id": 43281, "content": "玩电脑手生冻疮.", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 257793}, {"id": 43282, "content": "有一种思念叫望穿秋水，有一种冷叫忘穿秋裤～", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 436483}, {"id": 43538, "content": "骑完车后仿佛失去了自己的双手", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 390096}, {"id": 43283, "content": "万能的淘宝啊！！！我想买个太阳晒晒。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 25, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 436490}, {"id": 43284, "content": "我感觉自己的脊椎瘫痪了?", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 436492}, {"id": 43285, "content": "想起了老家东北的寒风凛冽，南方这算啥…", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 436502}, {"id": 44565, "content": "广东都敢下雪了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 441790}, {"id": 45845, "content": "在寒风中流的鼻涕被冰冻了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 451931}, {"id": 43286, "content": "原来火焰真的是生命之光.", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 356125}, {"id": 43798, "content": "广州都下雪了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 438954}, {"id": 43287, "content": "重庆下了雪 航班取了消:)", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 428636}, {"id": 45081, "content": "光身子跑来跑去穿着木屐吃麦旋风 热 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 447212}, {"id": 43546, "content": "北京22日晚已被吹成SB\n今天看见蓝天白云莫名傻笑", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 318005}, {"id": 43294, "content": "空调开到流鼻血也不会关", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 436545}, {"id": 43553, "content": "连广东都下雪了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 437626}, {"id": 45348, "content": "下班回家发现换下的衣服重量是自己体重的一半", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 449569}, {"id": 43304, "content": "鼻涕流挂脸上了也没有什么知觉", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 436603}, {"id": 43306, "content": "据说广州下雪了❄️", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 198497}, {"id": 43819, "content": "曾经在40℃的高温下说过宁愿被冻死也不愿被热死，直到昨天我才知道自己有多年少无知?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 437545}, {"id": 47147, "content": "内蒙人，当天在室外呆了一天，没风，感觉也就那样。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 458831}, {"id": 43308, "content": "家里玻璃窗上结了一层冰，是靠室内的这边", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 239090}, {"id": 49455, "content": "去肯德基取暖", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 467381}, {"id": 43824, "content": "这种天气还能让你出去的，只有真爱，至交，上班，上课这四元素了吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 375783}, {"id": 43314, "content": "家里这两只最不友善的猫因为寒冷依偎在一起", "image": "img/option/option/20160606145002Nyc54CkSlQ6ZzHOd.jpg", "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 436658}, {"id": 43059, "content": "今朝侬暖捏伐？", "image": null, "praise_count": 39, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 343013}, {"id": 43060, "content": "回到家开了空调，坐了半个小时之后才发现开的是制冷，居然没什么感觉，只是觉得风有点大，所以戴了戴帽子。", "image": null, "praise_count": 667, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 5}, {"id": 43572, "content": "昨天我又加了三条棉裤", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 404751}, {"id": 53300, "content": "烧钱去三亚避寒，遇上千年一遇的寒流，操。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 311407}, {"id": 43061, "content": "没感觉有什么特别", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 165652}, {"id": 43317, "content": "把冰箱里面的东西拿到外面来，冰箱关了省电些", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 436676}, {"id": 43062, "content": "情到浓时，抵近相吻。我说：不闭眼？你说：脸僵了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 172, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 431483}, {"id": 43318, "content": "就没感觉冷", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 344781}, {"id": 43063, "content": "站在雪中，感觉自己在演偶像剧", "image": null, "praise_count": 193, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 114979}, {"id": 43064, "content": "人在深圳也觉得，啊要穿2条裤子了，啊好想用个暖宝宝，啊我的手套围巾呢！", "image": null, "praise_count": 33, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 149477}]}